    "General traffic scene datasetsDuring the Development of autonomous driving, new algorithms have been introduced very quickly.",
    "Testing these algorithms on real vehicles is often a costly (and sometimes dangerous) task.",
    "With the rapid Development of machine learning-based algorithms for autonomous driving in recent years, large amounts of driving data are required for training and testing.",
    "Existing Automated Driving datasets are limited in one or more important aspects, including scene variations, annotation richness, and geographic distribution.",
    "In addition, models trained on existing datasets tend to be overly adapted to domain-specific features."
